To complete this task and enable the operation and shutdown of the lighting of the esp32 Wasdom piece, important steps were based on:
1. Open the arduino IDE program.
2. Connect the esp32 piece to a computer through an HD cord.
3. From the taskbar to choose a file, then examples, then WiFi, then wifiaccesspoint.
4. Modify the network name and password and enter html page data.
5. Download this process and wait for it to be completed.
6. Search for the name of the network in the computer and run it.
7. Open a browser Microsoft Edge and write type the IP address of the esp32 in search.
8. Here we are pushing to close.
9. Here we are pushing to run.
